select

public void select()
Perform all actions associated with selection. Flip the checked state (if checkable), execute the OnMenuItemClickListener (if available) or the Activity.onMenuItemSelected(int, MenuItem) that will call through to Activity.onOptionsItemSelected(MenuItem). The Intent will always be executed (if set).
